pullRequest.title: Add builder manual mode
pullRequest.bodyText:
Builders in manual mode don't automatically select build orders, but instead wait and let the player choose one for them.
This is how the build order selection looks like:

I would have liked to add the style to that menu too, however i don't think its worth it to add the style to WorkOrderView for that, or add a subclass of WorkOrderView adding that.
Changes proposed in this pull request:

Add a manual mode for builders that lets the player choose what they should build.
This can be toggled on the third page of the builders hut gui.


Review please

commit.message:
Add builder manual mode

Builders in manual mode don't automatically select build orders, but
instead wait and let the player choose one for them.
Add a chat message for when switching a builder to manual mode
